Happy birthday to the man of my dreams! 
I LOVE YOU 💕

Posting pictures from this stunning fall wedding from two years ago today, where I had the honor of being the bridesmaid. Here’s a photo dump because better late than never! 💕✨ #Memories #FallWeddingVibes #Bridesmaids

It was an absolute honor to serve as the lead architectural project manager for the renowned transit-oriented mixed-use project in Miami-Dade County, the largest development of its kind. Working alongside an exceptional team and acquiring a wealth of experience throughout this remarkable journey was an incredible opportunity that fills me with immense pride.

Devoting five years of my career to this endeavor proved to be truly worthwhile because of the positive impact it will have on our community. Now, I eagerly await my next challenge. Stay tuned!

I would love to hear from other new moms out there about their experiences and how they feel! 💕👶🏻 #NewMomLife #MotherhoodJourney #LoveAndChallenges #misspregnancy
